k — dependency injection point, not full integration.\n- Risk: AC #10 lane freeing tested indirectly via promise resolution.\n- Observation: Final story in epic 19. Validate step may be redundant with merge validation.\n\n## Token Report\n- Total tool calls: 15\n- By tool: Read: 8, Grep: 4, Glob: 4, Write: 1\n- Files read: 8 unique, 8 total reads\n- Redundant operations: None\n\n### 19-2-epic-flow-execution — dev-story (2026-04-04T03:24)\n\n- State machine gap: `epic-completion.ts` doesn't allow `completing -> done` directly. Empty/retro-only flows use `validating` initial state — subtle coupling between executor and caller.\n- No logging in retro skip path — no logger dependency available. Minor gap.\n\n## Token Report\n- Total tool calls: 19\n- By tool: Read: 6, Edit: 11, Bash: 4, Grep: 2, Write: 2\n- Largest Bash outputs: vitest run (~60 lines), npm test (~30 lines), npm run build (~20 lines)\n- Files read: 7 unique, 7 total reads\n- Redundant operations: none\n\n### 19-2-epic-flow-execution — verification (2026-04-04T03:44)\n\n- Proof already existed from prior session with ALL_PASS (12/12 ACs). Tier A quick-win — only needed `codeharness verify` validation.\n- No issues encountered.\n\n## Token Report\n- Total tool calls: 1 (subagent) + 3 (orchestrator)\n- By tool: Bash: 1 (codeharness verify)\n- Files read: 1 (proof document)\n- Redundant operations: none\n\n### 20-1-lane-container-lane-components — create-story (2026-04-04T03:47)\n\n- No config.yaml at expected path `_bmad/bmm/config.yaml`; found at `_bmad/config.yaml` instead.\n- All ACs are test-provable — pure presentational Ink components verified via ink-testing-library.\n- Risk: `ink-testing-library` availability — may need adding to devDependencies.\n- Observation: No existing Ink component test files — dev agent establishes the pattern.\n\n## Token Report\n- Total tool calls: 17\n- By tool: Read: 10, Glob: 5, Grep: 2, Bash: 1, Write: 1, Skill: 1\n- Largest Bash outputs: git log --oneline -10 (~10 line