reads\n- Redundant operations: 7 Edit calls for task checkboxes — could be fewer\n\n### 20-1-lane-container-lane-components — code-review (2026-04-04T06:25)\n\n- HIGH — H2: No integration tests for ink-app.tsx. AC #8, #10, #11 had zero test coverage at App integration level. Fixed: created ink-app.test.tsx with 6 tests.\n- HIGH — H3: Terminal resize not reactive. ink-app.tsx reads process.stdout.columns at render time but never subscribes to resize events. AC #12 partially implemented — belongs to story 20-3.\n- MEDIUM — M4 (fixed): Added thin separator between stacked full lanes for visual distinction.\n- LOW (unfixed): `truncate` degenerate behavior for maxLen < 4.\n- LOW (unfixed): LaneContainer with single lane shows \"Lane 1:\" label (guarded by ink-app.tsx).\n- Coverage gaps: no test for degenerate terminal width < 40, no e2e test for actual resize event propagation.\n- Architecture: circular dependency risk between ink-components.tsx ↔ ink-lane-container.tsx (currently safe via type-only imports).\n\n## Token Report\n- Total tool calls: 19\n- By tool: Bash: 6, Read: 10, Edit: 3, Grep: 2, Glob: 2, Write: 1, Skill: 1\n- Largest Bash outputs: full test suite (~20 lines), story tests (~10 lines), coverage check (~5 lines)\n- Files read: 12 unique, 13 total reads\n- Redundant operations: One Edit reverted (Separator import causing circular dep)\n","structuredPatch":[{"oldStart":326,"oldLines":3,"newStart":326,"newLines":31,"lines":[" - Largest Bash outputs: full test suite (~20 lines), story tests (~10 lines), coverage check (~5 lines)"," - Files read: 12 unique, 13 total reads"," - Redundant operations: One Edit reverted (Separator import causing circular dep)","+","+---","+","+# Session Issues Log — 2026-04-04 (session 7)","+","+### 20-1-lane-container-lane-components — verification (2026-04-04T02:42)","+","+- Tier A quick-win — proof already existed with ALL_PASS (12/12 ACs). Only needed `codeharness verify` validation.","+- No issues encountered.","+","+## Tok