l lanes for visual distinction.\n- LOW (unfixed): `truncate` degenerate behavior for maxLen < 4.\n- LOW (unfixed): LaneContainer with single lane shows \"Lane 1:\" label (guarded by ink-app.tsx).\n- Coverage gaps: no test for degenerate terminal width < 40, no e2e test for actual resize event propagation.\n- Architecture: circular dependency risk between ink-components.tsx ↔ ink-lane-container.tsx (currently safe via type-only imports).\n\n## Token Report\n- Total tool calls: 19\n- By tool: Bash: 6, Read: 10, Edit: 3, Grep: 2, Glob: 2, Write: 1, Skill: 1\n- Largest Bash outputs: full test suite (~20 lines), story tests (~10 lines), coverage check (~5 lines)\n- Files read: 12 unique, 13 total reads\n- Redundant operations: One Edit reverted (Separator import causing circular dep)\n\n---\n\n# Session Issues Log — 2026-04-04 (session 7)\n\n### 20-1-lane-container-lane-components — verification (2026-04-04T02:42)\n\n- Tier A quick-win — proof already existed with ALL_PASS (12/12 ACs). Only needed `codeharness verify` validation.\n- No issues encountered.\n\n## Token Report\n- Total tool calls: 1 (subagent)\n- By tool: Bash: 1\n- Files read: 1 (proof document in parent)\n- Redundant operations: none\n\n### 20-2-summary-bar-merge-status — create-story (2026-04-04T02:45)\n\n- No problems encountered. Epic definition clear.\n- Risk: AC #12 (single-lane hides SummaryBar/MergeStatus) — dev must not regress existing single-lane conditional logic in ink-app.tsx.\n- Observation: UX spec shows Ctrl+M toggling merge detail — scoped to 20-3, not this story.\n- Observation: Architecture doc lists ink-summary-bar.tsx and ink-merge-status.tsx as separate files.\n\n## Token Report\n- Total tool calls: 11\n- By tool: Read: 3, Grep: 5, Glob: 3, Write: 1\n- Files read: 4 unique, 4 total reads\n- Redundant operations: none\n","structuredPatch":[{"oldStart":354,"oldLines":3,"newStart":354,"newLines":14,"lines":[" - By tool: Read: 3, Grep: 5, Glob: 3, Write: 1"," - Files read: 4 unique, 4 to