{"type":"assistant","message":{"model":"claude-opus-4-6","id":"msg_012T6kWCPdCW4wcP9gj4cBGQ","type":"message","role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"tool_use","id":"toolu_01B9bUtRzLrujEZ2PDzFaDTd","name":"Write","input":{"file_path":"/Users/ivintik/dev/personal/codeharness/verification/20-2-summary-bar-merge-status-proof.md","content":"# Verification Proof: Story 20-2 Summary Bar & Merge Status\n\n**Story:** 20-2-summary-bar-merge-status\n**Date:** 2026-04-04\n**Tier:** test-provable\n**Result:** ALL_PASS (12/12 ACs)\n\n## Build & Test Summary\n\n| Check | Result |\n|-------|--------|\n| Build (`npm run build`) | PASS — tsup success, no errors |\n| Tests (`npm test`) | PASS — 5103 passed, 190 test files, 0 failures |\n| Lint (`npm run lint`) | 8 errors, 58 warnings (none in story files) |\n| Coverage | 96.79% statements (all files) |\n\n## Acceptance Criteria Verification\n\n### AC #1: SummaryBar component exports and renders summary format\n**Result:** PASS\n- **File exists:** `src/lib/ink-summary-bar.tsx` (2773 bytes)\n- **Exports:** `SummaryBarProps` interface, `MergingEpicInfo` interface, `SummaryBar` function component\n- **Props:** `doneStories`, `mergingEpic`, `pendingEpics`, `completedLanes`\n- **Tests passed:**\n  - \"exports SummaryBar as a function component\"\n  - \"renders done stories with checkmark symbols\"\n  - \"renders full summary with all sections populated\"\n  - \"exports correct types\"\n\n### AC #2: SummaryBar renders \"Merging: —\" when no merge active\n**Result:** PASS\n- **Test passed:** \"renders 'Merging: —' when no merge active\"\n\n### AC #3: SummaryBar renders merging epic with spinner when in-progress\n**Result:** PASS\n- **Test passed:** \"renders merging epic with spinner when in-progress\"\n\n### AC #4: SummaryBar renders resolving merge in yellow with conflict count\n**Result:** PASS\n- **Tests passed:**\n  - \"renders resolving merge with conflict count\"\n  - \"renders resolving merge with plural conflicts\"\n  - \"renders resolving merge without conflict count (omits parenthetical)\"\n\n### AC #5: MergeStatus component exports and renders merge progress\n**Result:** PASS\n- **File exists:** `src/lib/ink-merge-status.tsx` (3432 bytes)\n- **Exports:** `MergeState` interface, `MergeTestResults` interface, `MergeStatusProps` interface, `MergeStatus` function component\n- **Test passed:** \"exports MergeStatus as a function component\"\n\n### AC #6: MergeStatus renders clean merge in green\n**Result:** PASS\n- **Test passed:** \"renders clean merge in green\"\n\n### AC #7: MergeStatus renders resolved merge with file paths\n**Result:** PASS\n- **Tests passed:**\n  - \"renders resolved merge with file paths\"\n  - \"renders resolved merge with plural conflicts\"\n\n### AC #8: MergeStatus renders escalated merge in red\n**Result:** PASS\n- **Tests passed:**\n  - \"renders escalated merge in red with worktree path\"\n  - \"renders escalated merge without worktree path\"\n  - \"renders escalated with default reason when reason is missing\"\n\n### AC #9: MergeStatus renders test results\n**Result:** PASS\n- **Tests passed:**\n  - \"renders passing test results in green\"\n  - \"renders failing test results in red\"\n  - \"renders test results with coverage when available\"\n\n### AC #10: SummaryBar renders lane completion line\n**Result:** PASS\n- **Tests passed:**\n  - \"renders lane completion line\"\n  - \"renders multiple lane completion lines\"\n  - \"renders $0.00 for zero cost in lane completion\"\n\n### AC #11: ink-app.tsx integrates SummaryBar and MergeStatus between lanes and activity\n**Result:** PASS\n- **ink-app.tsx imports:** `SummaryBar` from `./ink-summary-bar.js`, `MergeStatus` from `./ink-merge-status.js`\n- **ink-components.tsx:** `RendererState` extended with `summaryBar?` and `mergeState?` fields\n- **Conditional rendering:** `laneCount > 1 && state.summaryBar` / `laneCount > 1 && state.mergeState`\n- **Separator lines:** present between sections\n- **Tests passed:**\n  - \"renders SummaryBar and MergeStatus when laneCount > 1 (AC #11)\"\n  - \"renders separator after SummaryBar/MergeStatus in multi-lane mode even without stories\"\n  - \"renders SummaryBar without MergeStatus when mergeState is absent\"\n\n### AC #12: Single lane mode does not render SummaryBar or MergeStatus\n**Result:** PASS\n- **Tests passed:**\n  - \"does NOT render SummaryBar or MergeStatus when laneCount <= 1 (AC #12)\"\n  - \"does NOT render SummaryBar or MergeStatus with no lanes (AC #12)\"\n\n## Files Verified\n\n| File | Status |\n|------|--------|\n| `src/lib/ink-summary-bar.tsx` | Created, exports SummaryBar + types |\n| `src/lib/ink-merge-status.tsx` | Created, exports MergeStatus + types |\n| `src/lib/__tests__/ink-summary-bar.test.tsx` | 16 tests, all passing |\n| `src/lib/__tests__/ink-merge-status.test.tsx` | 12 tests, all passing |\n| `src/lib/ink-app.tsx` | Modified, integrates both components |\n| `src/lib/ink-components.tsx` | Modified, RendererState extended |\n\n## Test Evidence\n\n- **ink-summary-bar.test.tsx:** 16 tests passed (0 failed)\n- **ink-merge-status.test.tsx:** 12 tests passed (0 failed)  \n- **ink-app.test.tsx:** 11 tests passed (0 failed), includes AC #11 and #12 integration tests\n- **Total project:** 5103 tests passed, 0 failed\n"},"caller":{"type":"direct"}}],"stop_reason":null,"stop_sequence":null,"stop_details":null,"usage":{"input_tokens":1,"cache_creation_input_tokens":264,"cache_read_input_tokens":39328,"cache_creation":{"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":264,"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":0},"output_tokens":1,"service_tier":"standard","inference_geo":"not_available"},"context_management":null},"parent_tool_use_id":"toolu_011YZbkZrGf2xqXyyhqeoeqK","session_id":"7e3ded59-6184-4f8b-8f55-ba5e63dae51f","uuid":"11132cef-9dfa-4abf-9ba6-1b57de86c5b7"}
